{"text_id":106466,"tokens":["The"," admis","sibility"," of"," a"," diary"," written"," by"," an"," accused"," person"," is"," a"," complex"," issue"," in"," criminal"," law","."," In"," many"," cases",","," diaries"," are"," considered"," admissible"," as"," evidence"," because"," they"," can"," provide"," important"," information"," about"," the"," accused","'","s"," state"," of"," mind",","," intentions",","," or"," even"," criminal"," actions","."," From"," a"," legal"," standpoint",","," a"," diary"," can"," be"," considered"," a"," written"," statement"," or"," declaration"," made"," by"," the"," accused",","," which"," can"," be"," used"," to"," impeach"," the"," accused","'","s"," credibility"," or"," provide"," evidence"," of"," a"," material"," fact",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," primary"," reasons"," diaries"," are"," admissible"," is"," because"," they"," are"," often"," considered"," an"," '","anti","cip","atory"," statement","'"," -"," a"," statement"," made"," by"," the"," accused"," before"," the"," alleged"," crime"," was"," committed","."," In"," the"," context"," of"," criminal"," law",","," anticip","atory"," statements"," are"," considered"," statements"," that"," predict"," or"," describe"," future"," events",","," and"," they"," can"," be"," used"," to"," prove"," intent",","," malice",","," or"," pre","meditation",".","\n\n","The"," courts"," have"," consistently"," held"," that"," diaries"," are"," not"," self","-","in","crimin","atory",","," even"," though"," they"," may"," contain"," in","crimin","ating"," statements","."," The"," reason"," for"," this"," is"," that"," the"," accused"," is"," not"," being"," forced"," to"," testify"," against"," themselves"," in"," the"," classical"," sense","."," Instead",","," the"," diary"," is"," considered"," an"," '","objective","'"," statement",","," independent"," of"," any"," physical"," or"," oral"," testimony"," by"," the"," accused",".","\n\n","In"," fact",","," the"," courts"," have"," recognized"," that"," a"," diary"," can"," be"," a"," valuable"," tool"," for"," the"," accused"," to"," provide"," an"," '","insider","'","s"," view","'"," of"," their"," own"," thoughts",","," feelings",","," and"," intentions","."," This"," can"," be"," particularly"," useful"," in"," cases"," where"," the"," accused"," claims"," to"," have"," been"," coer","ced"," or"," manipulated"," into"," committing"," the"," crime",".","\n\n","Of"," course",","," there"," are"," some"," limitations"," to"," the"," admis","sibility"," of"," diaries","."," For"," example",","," the"," diary"," may"," not"," be"," admitted"," if"," it"," is"," deemed"," to"," be"," unreliable"," or"," fabricated","."," Additionally",","," the"," courts"," may"," exclude"," certain"," parts"," of"," the"," diary"," if"," they"," are"," deemed"," to"," be"," irrelevant"," or"," hearsay",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," the"," admis","sibility"," of"," a"," diary"," written"," by"," an"," accused"," person"," is"," a"," nuanced"," issue"," that"," depends"," on"," a"," variety"," of"," factors","."," While"," it"," is"," true"," that"," a"," diary"," can"," be"," used"," to"," impeach"," the"," accused","'","s"," credibility",","," it"," is"," also"," an"," important"," tool"," for"," the"," accused"," to"," provide"," an"," '","insider","'","s"," view","'"," of"," their"," own"," thoughts"," and"," intentions","."," As"," such",","," diaries"," can"," be"," a"," valuable"," piece"," of"," evidence"," in"," criminal"," cases",","," and"," they"," should"," be"," carefully"," considered"," by"," both"," prosecutors"," and"," defense"," attorneys","."],"sub_source":"reddit","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}